metadata.name: I AM ART
metadata.description: This is a special 1/1. This piece represents who I am. This work art represents the sky isn’t the limit, anything is possible when you dare to dream big above anything and everything. Every object in this piece is a part of who I am and what makes me an artist and the things that inspire me everyday. This is me. My passion. My life. My love. My dreams. My soul. It’s who I am because at the end of the day, I AM ART.
